Being environmentally conscious isn't just for spotted owl huggers and granola eaters anymore. Going green has become the trend and Green Dub products help bring the green fad into your home. Made out of a wood fiber composite, Green Dub's products are recycleable, biodegradable, and have a very natural look, feel and smell. PEFC certified wood flour with German technology is used as raw material. This plant/ flower pot measures 5" and is ideal for small plants, flowers and herbs.
